
[1]statement

   STATEMENT, n.

   1. The act of stating, reciting or presenting verbally or on paper.

   2. A series of facts or particulars expressed on paper; as a written
   statement.

   3. A series of facts verbally recited; recital of the circumstances of
   a transaction; as a verbal statement.
